Azure Production Cost Estimation – Interview Ready
Scenario:
Azure Production environment in East US region with three virtual machines.


Infrastructure Requirement
- Number of VMs: 3
- Per VM Configuration:
  • CPU: 32 vCPUs
  • RAM: 128 GB
  • Disk: 1 TB Premium SSD (/data)
- OS: Linux


Recommended Azure VM Size
Standard_D32s_v5
- 32 vCPUs
- 128 GB RAM
- Best suited for balanced compute and memory workloads in production


